      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DARK GLEAM (7) was out of the money when resuming from a spell last start over 1200m at Emerald, beaten 2.75 lengths. Has a fair record when second up, including two top-three finishes. It doesn't get any easier but with added fitness he is capable of a big performance. SCHMOOZER (8) finished a 1.5 lengths fourth when resuming on a turf track at this track over 1000m then followed up with a solid second on dirt at Longreach over 1000m. Looks a strong chance to find winning form here. INQUISITIVE LEGEND (9) was in the money on the dirt at Longreach two runs ago then backed it up with a win, also on dirt, at Blackall over 1400m two weeks ago. Can measure up again. Shapes as one to consider. TAHKIAN BUBBLES (10) finished third last time over 1200m at Longreach, beaten 0.8 lengths. Meeting a tougher field but on her best form she is one of the key runners.",
